,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"히마리","body":"이게 뭐야! 엄청 엄청 맛있잖아!\n지금까지 마셔본 적 없을 정도로 향이 좋아!\n혹시 이거 굉장한 고급 차 아니야!?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"2022birthdayStory-006-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"란","body":"히마리가 생각하는 만큼 비싼 건 아니야.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"2022birthdayStory-006-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"히마리","body":"정말!? 엄청 비쌀 것 같은 향하고 맛이 나는데……\n토모에도 이거 마셔봐!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"2022birthdayStory-006-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"란","body":"그 차는 내가 요즘 빠져있는 녹차야.\n문하생이 선물로 줬었는데\n마셔보니까 산뜻해서 마시기 편하더라고.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nnf03","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"2022birthdayStory-006-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"